GORGEOUS 2 bed/2 bath in Luxury Pac Heights Bldng GOLDEN GATE VIEWS!!
descr: This incredibly LARGE and REMODELED 2 huge bedrooms with 2 large full bathrooms apartment home is located at 2140 Pacific Avenue in prime Pacific Heights. This 5th floor unit has INCREDIBLE Golden Gate Bridge  and city VIEWS!!! As you walk into your apartment you enter a large foyer which leads to the living room and separate dining room. The foyer and dining room have designer lighting fixtures in keeping with the buildings style and grace. The master bedroom has a large en-suite bathroom with separate bathtub and shower.  This unit also has lots of closet space (including a brand-new closet system in the master bedroom closet) and telecom system to allow guests to enter the building lobby. Enormous picture windows allow for tons of light.
